values: （身份或地位）相同的人，同辈；仔细看，凝视
To peer at something is to watch it carefully.
She peered at people through the window.
n. a person who belongs to the same age group or social group as someone else 同龄人，同地位的人
v. to look searchingly at something difficult to discern 凝视
vt. 封为贵族；与…同等 vi. 凝视，盯着看；窥视 n. 贵族；同等的人；同龄人
